parameters: A blood-red mutant is staring around in the middle of the garage...
\n<\n[2]>...In the end, is Yamashita still deceiving us?
\n<\n[3]>This sort of thing is almost becoming a habit...
Go upstairs to settle the score with Yamashita.
Yamashita, that guy... even in the end, he's still so cunning.
Are you trying to take the key from our corpses...?
Let's deal with this guy first, then go find him to get some answers.
What kind of twisted person would assign us such a monster?
Don't forget to retrieve the data on that level of the living quarters.
Go to the top floor and find Yamashita.
\n<\n[3]>He probably hasn't run yet; we still have time.
Barely managed to kill the mutant...
First, go to the living area on that level to retrieve the data.
Then head to the top floor to find Yamashita.
I can't anymore... my body... I can't move at all...
I... don't have the strength to stand up anymore...
I promised to escape with her...
